      <para role="TEXT">You can modify Biller by clicking the <guiicon
      moreinfo="none">Edit</guiicon> <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_edit.gif" role="ICON_EDIT"
                       width="4mm"/>
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject> icon in the right-hand column, or delete it by
      clicking the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Delete</guibutton>
      <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_trash.gif" role="ICON_TRASH"
                       width="4mm"/>
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject> icon.</para>

      <para role="TEXT">Cancel a transaction by clicking on the
      <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_makerchecker_cancel.gif"/>
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject> icon or approve by clicking the Action
      <inlinemediaobject>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata fileref="../images/icon_makerchecker_action.gif"/>
          </imageobject>
        </inlinemediaobject> icon. These icons are available if maker-checker
      is enabled for your profile.</para>

      <para role="TEXT">Click the <guibutton moreinfo="none">Add
      Biller</guibutton> button at the bottom of the list to add a
      Biller.</para>

      <para role="TEXT"><guiicon moreinfo="none">Edit</guiicon> and <guibutton
      moreinfo="none">Add</guibutton> display the same form, but in the case
      of <guibutton moreinfo="none">Edit</guibutton> it is preset with the
      details of the existing Biller. After entering the details, click
      <emphasis role="bold">Save</emphasis> at the bottom of the form.</para>

